arvard-and-upenn-pro-palestinian-protest-encampments/0000018f-9223-d212-abcf-d66fb96f0000</link><description>宾夕法尼亚大学的几名学生在试图占领校园建筑后等待重罪指控，而两名哈佛大学学生在新一波逮捕中被指控袭击和殴打</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 19:31:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/students-arrested-at-harvard-and-upenn-pro-palestinian-protest-encampments/0000018f-9223-d212-abcf-d66fb96f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列辛贝特安全部门邀请反内塔尼亚胡活动人士参加会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-shin-bet-security-service-brings-in-anti-netanyahu-activists-for-meeting/0000018f-91fa-d9d1-abcf-d7fefe0a0000</link><description>这些活动人士被召集到警察局参加“自愿会议”，消息人士称，这并不是为了威胁他们，而是为了“澄清法律界限”，并询问他们是否因抗议而受到威胁</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 19:20:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-shin-bet-security-service-brings-in-anti-netanyahu-activists-for-meeting/0000018f-91fa-d9d1-abcf-d7fefe0a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列侨民部长在马德里 Vox 会议上赞扬西班牙极右翼“与以色列结盟”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-diaspora-minister-praises-spains-far-right-vox-for-aligning-with-israel/0000018f-91bd-d212-abcf-d7fdfe550000</link><description>以色列的阿米猜·奇克利与极右翼同行玛丽娜·勒庞、乔治亚·梅洛尼、维克多·欧尔班、哈维尔·米莱和 Vox 的圣地亚哥·阿巴斯卡尔一起宣称，加沙战争“是一场针对西方文明的未来、反对激进伊斯兰教的生死存亡之战”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 17:37:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-diaspora-minister-praises-spains-far-right-vox-for-aligning-with-israel/0000018f-91bd-d212-abcf-d7fdfe550000</guid></item><item><title>“亲以色列”阴谋论者埃莉斯·斯特凡尼克来到以色列向特朗普求婚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-19/ty-article/.highlight/pro-israel-conspiracy-theorist-elise-stefanik-came-to-israel-to-court-trump/0000018f-91c4-d9a7-a9af-dbcef8a20000</link><description>与斯特凡尼克一样，绝大多数作为特朗普竞选搭档的潜在候选人公开出现的名字都倾向于全力支持以色列战争，同时攻击巴勒斯坦人和他们的支持者</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 17:30:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-19/ty-article/.highlight/pro-israel-conspiracy-theorist-elise-stefanik-came-to-israel-to-court-trump/0000018f-91c4-d9a7-a9af-dbcef8a20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和巴勒斯坦和平活动人士会见教皇，分享他们对共同未来的梦想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-palestinian-peace-activists-meet-pope-to-share-their-dream-of-a-shared-future/0000018f-9186-d212-abcf-d7efcfe30000</link><description>毛兹·伊农（Maoz Inon）的父母于 10 月 7 日被杀，阿齐兹·阿布·萨拉（Aziz Abu Sarah）在第二次起义中失去了弟弟，他们在 13,000 人面前向教皇方济各发表了讲话。教皇表示，他们的工作“不仅证明了对和平的渴望，而且是未来的计划”</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 16:47:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-palestinian-peace-activists-meet-pope-to-share-their-dream-of-a-shared-future/0000018f-9186-d212-abcf-d7efcfe30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 226 天：以色列国防军命令加沙北部拜特拉希亚居民撤离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-226-idf-orders-residents-in-north-gazas-beit-lahia-to-evacuate/0000018f-91b1-d9d1-abcf-d7fdbd860000</link><description>美国国家安全顾问沙利文正在以色列会见总理内塔尼亚胡和战时内阁部长甘茨 ■ 极右翼部长斯莫特里奇呼吁，如果真主党拒绝从边境撤军，以色列就占领加沙并入侵黎巴嫩南部 ■ 约旦外交部长呼吁调查此事他声称这是以色列在加沙战役期间犯下的战争罪 ■ 这是战争开始 226 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 16:35:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-226-idf-orders-residents-in-north-gazas-beit-lahia-to-evacuate/0000018f-91b1-d9d1-abcf-d7fdbd860000</guid></item><item><title>在取消和强烈抗议后，以色列耶路撒冷四重奏在阿姆斯特丹举行音乐会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/after-anti-israel-call-for-cancellation-jerusalem-quartet-plays-amsterdam-concert/0000018f-9110-d212-abcf-d77d8d9a0000</link><description>包括顶尖音乐家在内的超过 13,000 人签署了一份请愿书，呼吁阿姆斯特丹音乐厅允许耶路撒冷四重奏乐团进行演出，周六它也这样做了。音乐会和场外小型亲巴勒斯坦抗议活动顺利通过</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 15:56:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/after-anti-israel-call-for-cancellation-jerusalem-quartet-plays-amsterdam-concert/0000018f-9110-d212-abcf-d77d8d9a0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦消息人士明确表示，以色列支持的当地实体无法管理加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-sources-are-making-it-clear-that-no-israel-backed-local-entity-can-govern-gaza/0000018f-914b-d17a-a9df-915b5e5f0000</link><description>加沙的一位知名人士告诉《国土报》，“任何敢于执行这项任务的人都将是一名承包商，往好了说是无法承受压力，往坏了说是无法承受以色列的庇护”。然而，一项关于建立多国部队和外交进程的提议正在获得更多支持</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 15:45:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-19/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-sources-are-making-it-clear-that-no-israel-backed-local-entity-can-govern-gaza/0000018f-914b-d17a-a9df-915b5e5f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>